title: THE CRAZIEST HEADPHONES EVER
description:
Vinci Smart Headphones (USA Link) - http://amzn.to/2BeLufb
Vinci Smart Headphones (International) - http://geni.us/oXPr

The Vinci Smart headphones are quite unusual. They feature a display on the right ear cup, a SIM card slot, WIFI, Bluetooth and more. These headphones can operate in the absence of any smartphone using their own connectivity. Capable of playing music through local storage, Spotify, Soundcloud and Amazon. So are these headphones the future or just a gimmick?
